desc: Whether she's searching for her first horse or her first job; is saving for a down payment or an entry fee; is looking for the perfect jean or what to make for dinner, she needs a trailblazer. This is for her.

layout.text: A P L A C E F O R T R A I L B L A Z E R S

Annelle + James is where trailblazers get inspired. Whether she's looking for inspiration to help her get started or a community of girls to join her along the way, this is for her. Join us as we share stories and words from women who have dared to dream and are committed to making them come true.
